      <title>报告称中国考虑在 2025 年实施贬值货币 人民币下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/yuan-slides-on-report-china-considering-weaker-currency-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有报道称，北京方面正考虑明年允许人民币贬值，以应对与美国爆发贸易战的威胁，人民币因此出现一周内最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/yuan-slides-on-report-china-considering-weaker-currency-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 07:29:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
